➜节气英语丨「秋分」英语知识小百科
http://www.sohu.com/a/420092917_100171577	30830
<p>秋分是中国传统二十四节气中的第十六个节气。“秋分”的英文表达为Autumn Equinox，秋分过后，太阳直射点向南移动，北半球白昼时间变短，夜晚时间变长。</p>
<p>After that day, the location of direct sunlight moves to the south, making days shorter and nights longer in the northern hemisphere.</p>
<p>秋分的到来，预示着这一年已脱离夏的炎热，正式进入了秋季。关于秋分的习俗，你了解哪些呢？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200922/0a0a5488679b48808b156f9191bae5bf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>雨洗凉秋</strong></p>
<p>自秋分起，中国大部分地区已经进入了凉爽的秋季。此时田里的庄稼已经长得丰腴饱满，路边的梧桐叶子被季节染成一片暖黄。然而，与热情的颜色共生的，是淅淅沥沥，一场凉过一场的秋雨。</p>
<p>When the cold air southward meets the declining warm and wet air, precipitation is the result. The temperature also drops frequently.</p>
<p><strong>赏桂佳期</strong></p>
<p>秋分时节，正是赏桂花的好时节。这个时候，中国南方昼暖夜凉，所以人们白天穿单衣，温度变凉时就要加衣服。这段时期在汉语中被叫做“桂花蒸”，表示桂花绽放之时出现的闷热天气。</p>
<p>It is a good season to enjoy sweet-scented osmanthus full blossom around Autumn Equinox. At this time, it is hot in the day and cool in the night in South China, so people have to wear light clothing when it is hot, and put on more clothes when it is getting cooler. This period is named as "Guihuazheng" in Chinese, which means osmanthus mugginess.</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
