<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><strong>鲜蟹肥美</strong></p>
<p>这个时节的蟹是非常肥美的，民间素有“秋风起，蟹脚痒”一说。吃蟹可益阴补髓，清热解毒。</p>
<p>In this season, crabs are delicious. Eating crabs helps nourish the marrow and clear the heat inside the body.</p>
<p><strong>“竖蛋”游戏</strong></p>
<p>秋分这天，世界各地成千上万的人在参与“竖蛋”游戏。而相传这一习俗，起源于中国。“竖蛋”的诀窍是握住鸡蛋，使其蛋黄尽可能下沉。为了达成这个条件，最好选择生出来4-5天的鸡蛋，蛋黄更易沉降。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200922/10e10da17225406c9ddd9c18bad98505.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>On the Autumn Equinox day, there are thousands of people in the world trying to make eggs stand on end. And it is believed that this custom originated in China. The trick is holding the egg until the yolk sinks as much as possible. For this, you're better off choosing an egg of about 4 or 5 days old, whose yolk is easier to sink down.</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200922/2703564598c84186a92029d476297ee1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>